{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/(main)/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/layout,_N_T_/(main)/learn/[type]/[level]/page,_N_T_/learn/agent/beginner"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level/__PAGE__","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type/$d$level","/!KG1haW4p/learn/$d$type","/!KG1haW4p/learn","/!KG1haW4p","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0.q-h669a_dqa.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.16t1db8_9y2o~.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0.6dsdn7g3rv..css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14uv9l3-k2qh4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/16sk4~vc8e6sh.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0c9ih0_ge37cg.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-02v2juswviadt.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Agent 开发入门教程 - AI工具市场</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"学习 Agent 开发 的入门知识\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\"><header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white text-sm\">⚡</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">AI 工具市场</span></div></a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"relative w-72\"><div class=\"relative\"><svg class=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"全局搜索...\" class=\"w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div></div><a class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"学院\" href=\"/learn\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">🎓</span></a><a href=\"http://hsinky.cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"个人博客\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">📰</span></a></div></div></header><div class=\"flex\"><aside class=\"w-72 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 flex flex-col fixed left-0 top-14 h-[calc(100vh-56px)]\"><nav class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🏠</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">首页</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">概览与推荐</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/skill\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">✨</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Skill</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">可复用的能力模块</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/mcp\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔌</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">MCP</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">外部工具与服务接入</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🤖</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Agent</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">自主决策的AI助手</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/prompt\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📝</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Prompt</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">高效沟通的模板</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/workflow\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\">入门路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">Agent 开发</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Agent 开发</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">构建会自主思考的 AI</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->85分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>入门路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/agent/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/agent/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/agent/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>第一课：什么是 Agent？从 AI 助手到智能体</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">核心认知</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\"><strong>Agent（智能体）</strong>是具有<strong>自主决策能力</strong>的 AI 程序。它不只是回答问题，而是理解目标、规划步骤、执行任务，并基于结果调整策略。</p></div><div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3\">Agent vs 传统 AI 助手的本质区别</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-red-700\">传统 AI 助手</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 接收指令 → 返回答案</li><li>• 被动执行</li><li>• 无决策能力</li><li>• 像一个&quot;计算器&quot;</li></ul><div class=\"mt-3 bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs\">用户：&quot;帮我分析财报&quot; → AI 返回一段分析</div></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-green-700\">Agent</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 理解目标 → 自主规划 → 执行 → 反思</li><li>• 主动决策</li><li>• 可调用工具</li><li>• 像一个&quot;助手&quot;</li></ul><div class=\"mt-3 bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs\">用户：&quot;帮我分析财报&quot; → Agent: ①读取文件 ②提取数据 ③计算指标 ④生成报告</div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3 text-blue-700\">核心能力：四大模块</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\"></div><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">🧠 感知</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">理解用户意图，提取关键信息和约束条件</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\"></div><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">📋 规划</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">将目标分解为可执行的步骤</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\"></div><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">🔧 执行</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">调用工具和 Skill 完成任务</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border\"><div class=\"text-2xl mb-2\"></div><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">🔄 反思</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">评估结果，判断是否完成任务</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>第二课：Agent 工作流程</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">一个完整的 Agent 循环：</h4><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"font-mono text-sm\"><pre>1. 【输入】接收用户请求\n   ↓\n2. 【感知】理解意图和目标\n   - 提取：任务类型、约束条件、期望输出\n   ↓\n3. 【规划】生成行动计划\n   - 分解：复杂任务 → 简单步骤\n   - 排序：确定执行顺序\n   ↓\n4. 【执行循环】\n   while 任务未完成:\n       - 选择下一步行动\n       - 调用工具执行\n       - 获取执行结果\n       ↓\n5. 【反思】评估结果\n   - 检查：任务是否完成？\n   - 判断：是否需要调整策略？\n   ↓\n6. 【输出】返回最终结果</pre></div></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-green-700\">实战示例：分析财报</h4><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border text-sm space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">输入</span><p>&quot;帮我分析这份财报并生成报告&quot;</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-purple-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">规划</span><p>计划：①读取文件 ②提取财务数据 ③计算增长率 ④生成报告</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-green-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">执行</span><p>依次调用文件读取、数据提取、计算、报告生成工具</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-orange-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">反思</span><p>检查报告完整性，补充行业对比数据，生成最终报告</p></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-pink-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs flex-shrink-0\">输出</span><p>返回完整的财务分析报告</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">3</span>第三课：ReAct 框架</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3 text-purple-700\">ReAct = Reasoning（推理）+ Acting（行动）</h4><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-3\">ReAct 是最经典的 Agent 框架，它将&quot;思考&quot;和&quot;行动&quot;交替进行：</p><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border text-sm\"><p><strong>思考（Thought）</strong>：我需要查询当前时间</p><p><strong>行动（Action）</strong>：调用 get_current_time 工具</p><p><strong>观察（Observation）</strong>：2024-03-07 15:30:00</p><p><strong>思考</strong>：根据时间判断现在是工作时间</p><p><strong>行动</strong>：生成工作建议</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-700\">ReAct 的关键要素</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"p-2 bg-white rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">1. 思考（Thought）</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">分析当前情况，决定下一步要做什么</p></div><div class=\"p-2 bg-white rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">2. 行动（Action）</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">选择合适的工具执行操作</p></div><div class=\"p-2 bg-white rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">3. 观察（Observation）</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">获取工具执行的结果</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">ReAct Prompt 模板</h4><div class=\"font-mono text-xs\"><pre>你是一个能使用工具的智能助手。\n\n# 可用工具\n{{tools}}\n\n# 工作流程\n对于每个步骤：\n1. Thought: 思考下一步要做什么\n2. Action: 选择工具执行\n3. Observation: 观察执行结果\n\n# 示例\nUser: 北京现在几点？\nThought: 我需要查询当前北京时间\nAction: get_current_time\nObservation: 15:30:00\nThought: 我已经获取到时间\nFinal Answer: 北京现在是 15:30:00\n\n# 你的任务\n{{task}}\n\n# 开始！</pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->入门路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><scri